ion+Revolution\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Orgill-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Orgill_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Klan, Anthony (8 July 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/ber-waste-tops-15b/story-fn59niix-1226090622303\">\"BER waste tops $1.5&#160;billion\"</a>. <i>The Australian</i>. Brisbane<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 July</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Australian&amp;rft.atitle=BER+waste+tops+%241.5+billion&amp;rft.date=2011-07-08&amp;rft.aulast=Klan&amp;rft.aufirst=Anthony&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fnational-affairs%2Fber-waste-tops-15b%2Fstory-fn59niix-1226090622303&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABuilding+the+Education+Revolution\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Keane, Bernard (5 May 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.crikey.com.au/2010/05/05/read-all-about-it-the-ber-program-worked-and-worked-well/\">\"Read all about it: the BER program worked, and worked well\"</a>. <i>Crikey</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">23 June</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Crikey&amp;rft.atitle=Read+all+about+it%3A+the+BER+program+worked%2C+and+worked+well&amp;rft.date=2010-05-05&amp;rft.aulast=Keane&amp;rft.aufirst=Bernard&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crikey.com.au%2F2010%2F05%2F05%2Fread-all-about-it-the-ber-program-worked-and-worked-well%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABuilding+the+Education+Revolution\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.anao.gov.au/Publications/Audit-Reports/2009-2010/Building-the-Education-Revolution---Primary-Schools-for-the-21st-Century\">\"Building the Education Revolution \u2013 Primary Schools for the 21st Century\"</a>. Australian National Audit Office<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">23 June</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Building+the+Education+Revolution+%E2%80%93+Primary+Schools+for+the+21st+Century&amp;rft.pub=Australian+National+Audit+Office&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.anao.gov.au%2FPublications%2FAudit-Reports%2F2009-2010%2FBuilding-the-Education-Revolution---Primary-Schools-for-the-21st-Century&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABuilding+the+Education+Revolution\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Stiglitz-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Stiglitz_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2010/08/06/2975865.htm\">\"Stimulus 'served Australia well' despite waste\"</a>. <i>ABC news</i>. Australian Broadcasting Corporation. 10 August 2010<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">24 March</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajou